name: Trencher
description: Trencher (TRENCHER) is a meme cryptocurrency on the Solana network, born from a viral satirical illustration by the artist Grizzle (known as @grizzle_art on X) that humorously depicted the Solana “Pump” ecosystem​followin.io . The meme resonated with the Solana community, leading enthusiasts to create the Trencher token as a homage and to support the original artist. Trencher’s identity centers around the eponymous cartoon character “Trencher,” and the project’s official website even features a Trencher image generator to encourage community creativity and engagement (allowing users to create their own Trencher-themed artwork).
